<p>这里需要计算 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>E</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>γ</mi><mrow><mi>j</mi><mi>k</mi></mrow></msub><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">E(\gamma_{jk})</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.0361em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05556em;">γ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3361em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0556em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">jk</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>，记为响应度 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mover accent="true"><mi>γ</mi><mo>^</mo></mover><mrow><mi>j</mi><mi>k</mi></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\hat \gamma _{jk}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.9805em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord accent"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.6944em;"><span style="top:-3em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05556em;">γ</span></span><span style="top:-3em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="accent-body" style="left:-0.25em;"><span class="mord">^</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1944em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3361em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0556em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">jk</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p class="katex-block"><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mtable width="100%"><mtr><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mtable rowspacing="0.25em" columnalign="right left" columnspacing="0em"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><msub><mover accent="true"><mi>γ</mi><mo>^</mo></mover><mrow><mi>j</mi><mi>k</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mi>E</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>γ</mi><mrow><mi>j</mi><mi>k</mi></mrow></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>y</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mo lspace="0em" rspace="0em">=</mo></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>γ</mi><mrow><mi>j</mi><mi>k</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>y</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mo lspace="0em" rspace="0em">=</mo></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>γ</mi><mrow><mi>j</mi><mi>k</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>K</mi></munderover><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>γ</mi><mrow><mi>j</mi><mi>k</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mo lspace="0em" rspace="0em">=</mo></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mstyle mathcolor="red"><msub><mi>γ</mi><mrow><mi>j</mi><mi>k</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>θ</mi><mstyle mathcolor="black"><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mstyle mathcolor="green"><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>γ</mi><mrow><mi>j</mi><mi>k</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mstyle></mstyle></mstyle></mrow><mrow><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>K</mi></munderover><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><msub><mi>γ</mi><mrow><mi>j</mi><mi>k</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>γ</mi><mrow><mi>j</mi><mi>k</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mo lspace="0em" rspace="0em">=</mo></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel="0" displaystyle="true"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mfrac><mstyle mathcolor="green"><msub><mi>α</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mstyle mathcolor="black"><mi>ϕ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mstyle mathcolor="red"><msub><mi>θ</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mstyle></mstyle></mstyle><mrow><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>K</mi></munderover><msub><mi>α</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mi>ϕ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><msub><mi>θ</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable></mtd><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mtext>(31)</mtext></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\begin{aligned}
\hat \gamma _{jk}= &amp;E(\gamma_{jk}|y,\theta)\\
=&amp;P(\gamma_{jk}=1|y,\theta)\\
=&amp;\frac{P(\gamma_{jk}=1,y_j|\theta)}{\sum_{k=1}^KP(\gamma_{jk}=1,y_j|\theta)}\\
=&amp;\frac{P(y_j|\color{red}\gamma_{jk}=1,\theta\color{black})\color{green}P(\gamma_{jk}=1|\theta)}{\sum_{k=1}^KP(y_j|\gamma_{jk}=1,\theta)P(\gamma_{jk}=1|\theta)}\\
=&amp;\frac{\color{green}\alpha_k\color{black}\phi(y_j|\color{red}\theta_k)}{\sum_{k=1}^K\alpha_k\phi(y_j|\theta_k)}\tag{31}
\end{aligned}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:11.6938em;vertical-align:-5.5969em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mtable"><span class="col-align-r"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:6.0969em;"><span style="top:-8.6839em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.427em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord accent"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.6944em;"><span style="top:-3em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05556em;">γ</span></span><span style="top:-3em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="accent-body" style="left:-0.25em;"><span class="mord">^</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1944em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3361em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0556em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">jk</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span></span></span><span style="top:-7.1839em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.427em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mrel">=</span></span></span><span style="top:-5.0969em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.427em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mrel">=</span></span></span>